{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4359f2c630","title":"中国人民解放军北京市公安局军事管制委员会布告","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c5a6199ea0","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":11,"articleId":"4359f2c630","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"公安与法律","id":"53b954d860","type":"主题"},{"name":"地方军管会、地方军区","id":"58a1d436cf","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"宣言","id":"5bfa9ca15d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a7d857fe54","type":"title","text":"中国人民解放军北京市公安局军事管制委员会布告","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4359f2c630","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8dbdddc359","type":"paragraph","text":"为了切实贯彻执行伟大领袖毛主席提出的“抓革命、促生产”的方针，加强街道交通管理，维护首都的革命秩序，保卫无产阶级文化大革命，特规定：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4359f2c630","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1bbddd0b7d","type":"paragraph","text":"一、各种车辆的驾驶人员和行人，要自觉维护交通秩序，严格遵守交通规则，听从人民警察的指挥。所有的家长都应教育自己的子女，模范地遵守交通规则。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4359f2c630","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71e3ec4e91","type":"paragraph","text":"二、严禁无驾驶执照的人员开车。不准乱开别人的车辆，不准擅自挪用各种车辆的牌照。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4359f2c630","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b0a86128d","type":"paragraph","text":"三、各种车辆不许在禁止通行的地区行驶，通过路口时不准抢行。骑自行车不准带人。在城区主要街道两侧的人行道上，不准乱放自行车和其他车辆。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4359f2c630","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8c46ca389b","type":"paragraph","text":"四、不准利用正在行驶的各种车辆散发传单，以免发生事故。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4359f2c630","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd51001d59","type":"paragraph","text":"五、禁止倒卖和倒换各种纪念章、语录牌、照片、报纸及其他材料。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4359f2c630","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb1fe3e5c0","type":"paragraph","text":"希各机关、院校、厂矿、企业、各革命群众组织积极行动起来，对所属人员广泛宣传教育，大力协助维护首都的革命秩序。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4359f2c630","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4f979575a9","type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民解放军北京市公安局军事管制委员会","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4359f2c630","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f04123b7e","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年四月十一日","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4359f2c630","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}